        <description>&lt;img src="https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU1rYWNueFNwQXlXVlh2SmpGVklndFc3czBDb2ZnQUF1b01heHQtazFGV1djOHh1MWoyZXdvQkFBTUNBQU4zQUFNNkJBIiwiZSI6InBuZyIsIm4iOiJwYXN0ZV8xNzc0ODQyMTg0MTY3LnBuZyIsIm0iOiJpbWFnZS9wbmciLCJzIjoxMTA5NjgwLCJ0IjoxNzc0ODQyMTg3MDM5LCJtaWQiOjM2fQ.RDDIGcTlsfo3QFfRptX4MRbwu4ht4pkbkEJWXEvS6UI.png" alt="Featured image of post 【Hugo】Hugo &#43; Github 免费部署自己的博客" /&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;hugohugo--github-免费部署自己的博客&#34;&gt;【Hugo】Hugo + Github 免费部署自己的博客
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;使用 hugo 工具生成静态页面，然后在 github 上部署静态页面，来免费搭建自己的博客。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-环境准备&#34;&gt;1 环境准备
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;11-git-下载&#34;&gt;1.1 Git 下载
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;前往【&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://git-scm.com&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Git 官网&lt;/a&gt;】，下载安装程序。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;一直点下一步，默认安装即可。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU1tYWNueGRnQUJoSF9oOW0tZVdROE5yUWxSdFZKRkFBTHJER3NiZnBOUlZtRHRlV3pkelRxekFRQURBZ0FEZVFBRE9nUSIsImUiOiJwbmciLCJuIjoicGFzdGVfMTc3NDg0MjIyNzg3MS5wbmciLCJtIjoiaW1hZ2UvcG5nIiwicyI6MzI2MjE3LCJ0IjoxNzc0ODQyMjMwMzc3LCJtaWQiOjM4fQ.ImWys8sS17hoDONgChuGEhGHpnMBQB5POc-eKP4_W2Y.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;paste_1774842227871.png&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;12-hugo-下载&#34;&gt;1.2 Hugo 下载
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;前往【&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/tags&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Hugo Github Tags&lt;/a&gt;】，选择对应版本下载，下载后解压即可。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Windows 下载版本&lt;/strong&gt;：&lt;code&gt;hugo_extended_xxxxx_windows_amd64.zip&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU1vYWNueHFLRVZwcVpJQ3N3NllFRDNDaDdmUTFVQUF1d01heHQtazFGV1JhLWtHdFI0UHZFQkFBTUNBQU41QUFNNkJBIiwiZSI6InBuZyIsIm4iOiJwYXN0ZV8xNzc0ODQyMjgwNTQ3LnBuZyIsIm0iOiJpbWFnZS9wbmciLCJzIjo1MDUwMywidCI6MTc3NDg0MjI4MTExMiwibWlkIjo0MH0.DszTtcxShWnXRUT1_w9x-DKDGz73soU9sRCRPRUZ174.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;paste_1774842280547.png&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-搭建博客&#34;&gt;2 搭建博客
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;21-创建博客&#34;&gt;2.1 创建博客
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;在 &lt;code&gt;hugo.exe&lt;/code&gt; 所在文件夹的地址栏输入 &lt;code&gt;cmd&lt;/code&gt;，按 &lt;code&gt;Enter&lt;/code&gt; 唤起命令行。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU1xYWNueHd0NkluQUtjQXRoWTZOeDNZV3dOcms0QUF1ME1heHQtazFGV2RJSjNQRzlTOUo0QkFBTUNBQU41QUFNNkJBIiwiZSI6InBuZyIsIm4iOiJwYXN0ZV8xNzc0ODQyMzA2NTM1LnBuZyIsIm0iOiJpbWFnZS9wbmciLCJzIjoyOTA4NCwidCI6MTc3NDg0MjMwNjQ5MywibWlkIjo0Mn0.K9qvRaZ0vdzJ0ntQ_hHNVoeVTLPWbEiCTNnhEZrhZRI.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;paste_1774842306535.png&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;输入命令 &lt;code&gt;hugo new site xxxx&lt;/code&gt; 创建 hugo 项目文件。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU1zYWNueDNMWjJvMndMRVBnSlRRQUJham5GV0MtNEFBTHVER3NiZnBOUlZpYWxETmtYTjQxVkFRQURBZ0FEZVFBRE9nUSIsImUiOiJwbmciLCJuIjoicGFzdGVfMTc3NDg0MjMzMjYzNS5wbmciLCJtIjoiaW1hZ2UvcG5nIiwicyI6MjY2NDIsInQiOjE3NzQ4NDIzMzI2MTYsIm1pZCI6NDR9.4gP3Zgkk2eY7VNBo9lk07z2dyZ1T90WrpZ14QlJ7JaA.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;paste_1774842332635.png&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;输入命令 &lt;code&gt;cd xxxx&lt;/code&gt; 切换目录，并将 &lt;code&gt;hugo.exe&lt;/code&gt; 复制到刚生成的文件夹中。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU11YWNueDhzWkQtMXNHU1o0dGNMNVZMbElQbjg0QUF1OE1heHQtazFGV1JXSG92cVBqZERzQkFBTUNBQU41QUFNNkJBIiwiZSI6InBuZyIsIm4iOiJwYXN0ZV8xNzc0ODQyMzU0NjU2LnBuZyIsIm0iOiJpbWFnZS9wbmciLCJzIjo2MzQ3OCwidCI6MTc3NDg0MjM1NDcxMCwibWlkIjo0Nn0.4qY8j_WNkKZhmu_DPQ3hF10StkiDgloXNiglzHfYEjQ.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;paste_1774842354656.png&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;输入命令 &lt;code&gt;hugo server -D&lt;/code&gt; 启动服务，访问 [http://localhost:1313]。按 &lt;code&gt;Ctrl+C&lt;/code&gt; 可停止服务。
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;(注意：hugo 默认没有主题，需要进行主题配置)&lt;/em&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU13YWNueUFVMHhSVDlzUi1OTll5U0V6a1h6aG5zQUF2QU1heHQtazFGV2pDNm9KTjgwYTlvQkFBTUNBQU41QUFNNkJBIiwiZSI6InBuZyIsIm4iOiJwYXN0ZV8xNzc0ODQyMzY5MjcyLnBuZyIsIm0iOiJpbWFnZS9wbmciLCJzIjo0MzcxMCwidCI6MTc3NDg0MjM2OTI1OCwibWlkIjo0OH0.g2jB34r7QFXXrx7XZq4k8vqyfzNF-y44vALmdo1c_UY.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;paste_1774842369272.png&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;22-配置主题&#34;&gt;2.2 配置主题
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;前往【&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://themes.gohugo.io&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Hugo Themes&lt;/a&gt;】，查找并下载喜欢的主题。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU15YWNueUV4YkZHMDBrV0NLSmlKc2FFd05hUUdNQUF2SU1heHQtazFGV3pKT3lhdWlwejlzQkFBTUNBQU41QUFNNkJBIiwiZSI6InBuZyIsIm4iOiJwYXN0ZV8xNzc0ODQyMzg2OTk0LnBuZyIsIm0iOiJpbWFnZS9wbmciLCJzIjoxNTM3MDYsInQiOjE3NzQ4NDIzODc1NTEsIm1pZCI6NTB9.-kird77-G0zhERdxmyGcev3jrTv9qFnf8irSgUrIcXk.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;paste_1774842386994.png&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;以 &lt;strong&gt;Stack 主题&lt;/strong&gt; 为例：将下载好的主题解压，放到 &lt;code&gt;/themes&lt;/code&gt; 文件夹中。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU0wYWNueUlqdmVNMXdqUTRGVnhTaVBzMXQ4SXhZQUF2TU1heHQtazFGV2Nrb1RvemZlNE44QkFBTUNBQU41QUFNNkJBIiwiZSI6InBuZyIsIm4iOiJwYXN0ZV8xNzc0ODQyNDAyNjc5LnBuZyIsIm0iOiJpbWFnZS9wbmciLCJzIjo3NTcwMCwidCI6MTc3NDg0MjQwMjkwMywibWlkIjo1Mn0.EHHntOmAIvo4xcaM-0KI-mUchK3Yh5H937aVdGSGfjM.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;paste_1774842402679.png&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;将 &lt;code&gt;exampleSite&lt;/code&gt; 样例数据中的 &lt;code&gt;content&lt;/code&gt; 和 &lt;code&gt;hugo.yaml&lt;/code&gt; 复制到主文件夹中，并删掉原有的 &lt;code&gt;hugo.toml&lt;/code&gt; 和 &lt;code&gt;content/post/rich-content&lt;/code&gt;。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU0yYWNueU1obVhxd3BBNm5YN181cDBLZEViWWkwQUF2VU1heHQtazFGV3poZEl3RzAyOVNFQkFBTUNBQU41QUFNNkJBIiwiZSI6InBuZyIsIm4iOiJwYXN0ZV8xNzc0ODQyNDE5MTMxLnBuZyIsIm0iOiJpbWFnZS9wbmciLCJzIjozNzE1NiwidCI6MTc3NDg0MjQxOTEyMCwibWlkIjo1NH0.PkZHqCPgBmaE_N4YE2EO7QWklTrwspeo4tnf4n5MNCk.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;paste_1774842419131.png&#34;
	
	
&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU00YWNueU5wNjZ6SmFSRlNjd1RPS05aV3M4YThVQUF2WU1heHQtazFGV1NUbWkzU0FPTmo4QkFBTUNBQU41QUFNNkJBIiwiZSI6InBuZyIsIm4iOiJwYXN0ZV8xNzc0ODQyNDIyNzU1LnBuZyIsIm0iOiJpbWFnZS9wbmciLCJzIjozMjU1NSwidCI6MTc3NDg0MjQyMjczNiwibWlkIjo1Nn0.YgS1vvMdYmMVJ1CjM9iW_3IaD5LEpDo22eZwYNmJn7Y.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;paste_1774842422755.png&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;修改 &lt;code&gt;hugo.yaml&lt;/code&gt; 中的 &lt;code&gt;theme&lt;/code&gt; 字段，确保其值与主题文件夹名称一致。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU02YWNueWF5NTc5azJ2U0pER044bVhjd3QtMHNNQUF2Y01heHQtazFGV3BHMUNhNnc0UEZnQkFBTUNBQU41QUFNNkJBIiwiZSI6InBuZyIsIm4iOiJwYXN0ZV8xNzc0ODQyNDc1NjY3LnBuZyIsIm0iOiJpbWFnZS9wbmciLCJzIjo1MzkzNSwidCI6MTc3NDg0MjQ3NTY5MywibWlkIjo1OH0.cvtxqHI3RwqjyuYcEhoiuUlgVnxP2ggt3INes5zT_18.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;paste_1774842475667.png&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;再次启动 hugo 服务查看效果。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU04YWNueWVqV3ppTzh0bHZnajNVYU9vZVRORGI4QUF2a01heHQtazFGV09Sa1dURFN5MUpnQkFBTUNBQU41QUFNNkJBIiwiZSI6InBuZyIsIm4iOiJwYXN0ZV8xNzc0ODQyNDkwNDQ4LnBuZyIsIm0iOiJpbWFnZS9wbmciLCJzIjoxOTg0NzYsInQiOjE3NzQ4NDI0OTEwNTMsIm1pZCI6NjB9.HR8Yg8sJ_7BzcJcprnGz6gixQedTafFVZMWBxKLbLdA.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;paste_1774842490448.png&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;3-github-部署&#34;&gt;3 Github 部署
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;31-常规部署&#34;&gt;3.1 常规部署
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;前往【&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Github 官网&lt;/a&gt;】，创建仓库，命名为 &lt;code&gt;{github用户名}.github.io&lt;/code&gt;。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU0tYWNueTNESzhMUVlNamdBQjhfQ2RKT2c4ZlZud0FBTDdER3NiZnBOUlZvVFFpLS1MZVYzUUFRQURBZ0FEZVFBRE9nUSIsImUiOiJwbmciLCJuIjoicGFzdGVfMTc3NDg0MjU4ODg1OS5wbmciLCJtIjoiaW1hZ2UvcG5nIiwicyI6MzIyODEsInQiOjE3NzQ4NDI1ODg4NTIsIm1pZCI6NjJ9.Go70I-1ydlJuIaG5O0nNtJdtkJLmtGvgicLuMUB4bvk.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;paste_1774842588859.png&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;进入仓库 &lt;code&gt;Settings -&amp;gt; Pages -&amp;gt; Branch&lt;/code&gt;，选择 &lt;code&gt;main&lt;/code&gt; 分支并保存。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU5BYWNueS1BTlRybUNLSzZzbVpQQ3QtQWlHak1ZQUF2d01heHQtazFGVzN3N0FLMVlwMnJvQkFBTUNBQU41QUFNNkJBIiwiZSI6InBuZyIsIm4iOiJwYXN0ZV8xNzc0ODQyNjE1OTUwLnBuZyIsIm0iOiJpbWFnZS9wbmciLCJzIjo4NTk5OSwidCI6MTc3NDg0MjYxNjY5MSwibWlkIjo2NH0.ntbVxtS6Opu8nSBxXoDjFRqKLFFv_zBeTB4ww9eGk0M.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;paste_1774842615950.png&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;在本地 hugo 项目文件夹中执行 &lt;code&gt;hugo -D&lt;/code&gt;，生成 &lt;code&gt;public&lt;/code&gt; 静态资源文件夹。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://k-vault-dvo.pages.dev/file/tgs_eyJ2IjoxLCJmIjoiQWdBQ0FnVUFBeUVHQUFUZUVRN1RBQU5DYWNuekJpYjRsUTAwUm53NVNUQUx4bEV6LTA0QUF2ME1heHQtazFGV0tObFFTYWlzNjhnQkFBTUNBQU41QUFNNkJBIiwiZSI6InBuZyIsIm4iOiJwYXN0ZV8xNzc0ODQyNjI5NDg0LnBuZyIsIm0iOiJpbWFnZS9wbmciLCJzIjo5NTExMywidCI6MTc3NDg0MjYzMDUzOSwibWlkIjo2Nn0.sggkLH2nxsUc4lGX1uOqSW_P4ZRhKK0o676I3CXZdOU.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;paste_1774842629484.png&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;在 &lt;code&gt;public&lt;/code&gt; 文件夹内执行以下命令上传到 Github：
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;5
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;6
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git init
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git add .
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git commit -m &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;first commit&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git branch -M main
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git remote add origin &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;你的github仓库地址&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git push -u origin main
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;访问 &lt;code&gt;https://{github用户名}.github.io&lt;/code&gt; 即可查看博客。&lt;/li&gt;
